    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years of age or younger at the onset of disease

          -  Presence of Vascular Thrombosis

          -  UC Davis patient

          -  Presence of at least one Laboratory criteria including: Anticardiolipin antibody,
             Anti-B glycoprotein-I antibody or Lupus anticoagulant in plasma

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Infants born to mothers with APS

          -  Infants with congenital thrombophilia
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
